17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
18 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
19 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 4810 of Title 36, unless there
20 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
21 In rural fire departments, fire insurance policies shall provide
22 coverage in all residential or dwelling policies for a fire
23 department response at a minimum of two percent (2%) of the property
24 value. The fire department response fee shall be One Thousand
